{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/MagicolorLogoEn.png?t=1707349760\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/Label.png?t=1707349760\" /><br><br><br>Color System - MagiColor Gameplay:<br><br>A clever color strategy can often outperform sheer power. Even the strongest stats can fall short if they're not the right color. Typically, only matching colors trigger effects, while mismatched ones are immune. You can shift the battlefield dynamics by altering your own or your enemies' colors.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/color.png?t=1707349760\" />  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/EngPoint.png?t=1707349760\" /><br> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/CloudTower.png?t=1707349760\" /> <br><br>Towers and Characters (MagiColor Summons):<br><br>Each character and tower is uniquely hand-drawn, with its own style of attack. Arrange them to suit your strategy or personal taste.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/Succubus.gif?t=1707349760\" />          <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/King.gif?t=1707349760\" />  <br><br><br> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/Tower.png?t=1707349760\" /> <br><br><br>  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/Wizard.gif?t=1707349760\" />             <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/Archer.gif?t=1707349760\" /> <br><br>Magic Items - (MagiColor Artifacts):<br><br>With nearly 20 unique items, the game offers a wide range of strategic options and fun, fueling your creativity.<br> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/artifact.png?t=1707349760\" /><br><br>MagiColor Slimes:<br><br>There are nearly 20 types of slimes, each with its own quirks. Some are fast, others have more health, and the most challenging ones often have special effects due to sharing colors with your forces. Blindly attacking can sometimes backfire.<br> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/Slime.png?t=1707349760\" /><br><br>MagiColor Encyclopedia:<br><br>A detailed encyclopedia is at your disposal, filled with all the information you need about the game's mechanics and lore.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/encyclopaedia.png?t=1707349760\" /><br><br>Hero Mode:<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/extras/Mod.png?t=1707349760\" /><br>After conquering the adventure mode, Hero Mode awaits. Here, you start with your initial health and resources, and you can mix and match an array of unlimited-use artifacts along with five new MagiColor Vortexes. Your challenge is to progress from the very first level straight to the last.<br><br>Health and MagiColor resources are carried over from start to finish.<br>All MagiColor Summons and features are unlocked right from the start.<br>Choose any five artifacts without any usage limits.<br>Five new global skills, the MagiColor Vortexes, offer substantial support on the battlefield.<br>Full access to MagiColor Marks.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1707349760","bac